				<td colspan="2"><span>April 21st, 2004 
<br />
---------------------- 
<br />

<br />
Headlines! 
<br />
- Boat Gnomes are now available all the time. (and I thought gnomes were only good as appetizers) 
<br />
- A new edition of the newspaper is available in your home town. Come and get it! 
<br />

<br />

<br />
Boat gnomes 
<br />
---------------------- 
<br />

<br />
The boat gnomes and other alternate means of travel are now available. During this period of gnome servitude, the boats will be in drydock and receiving some much needed repairs</span></td>
