<br />

<br />
I have been in game for hours now with petition in place and no response.
<br />

<br />
This morning, I had no idea a patch was coming, I was in DSP doing rockhoppers as is my want.  I died, couldn't find a cleric so looted all but one item and tried again, died again.  Oh well, I'll just get rez'd when I get back on.  Corpse ages, less than 30 min at time I logged off.
<br />

<br />
Game comes back up, I get in game with alt to look for someone to rez me, I go check on my corpses.  OMFG, NO!!!! My corpse with my gear on it shows nekkid, as do all other corpses around me that were there and dressed prior to patch.  Even worse, my rez timer on first corpse has expired, my second corpse rez timer is about to.  I got one rez but left both bodies.
<br />

<br />
I'm still waiting, and very frustrated.</span></td>
